query:
UPDATE postgres_trigger 
            SET 
                postgres_resource_path = $1,
                replication_slot_name = $2,
                publication_name = $3,
                script_path = $4,
                path = $5,
                is_flow = $6,
                edited_by = $7,
                email = $8,
                edited_at = now(),
                server_id = NULL,
                error = NULL,
                error_handler_path = $11,
                error_handler_args = $12,
                retry = $13
            WHERE 
                workspace_id = $9 AND path = $10
